\paragraph{Overview} 
We design task-specific prompts for the LLM that explore two IE variants for graph construction.
In the first variant, termed Neon({{arxiv_2411_12449_FO0022||FO}}), LLM generates news entity-interactions {{arxiv_2411_12449_FO0023||FO}} using only the subject {{arxiv_2411_12449_FO0024||FO}} and the corresponding news chunk {{arxiv_2411_12449_FO0025||FO}} that mentions {{arxiv_2411_12449_FO0026||FO}}. In the second variant, {{arxiv_2411_12449_FO0027||FO}} is generated by incorporating both the subject {{arxiv_2411_12449_FO0028||FO}} and object {{arxiv_2411_12449_FO0029||FO}} entities, along with the news chunk {{arxiv_2411_12449_FO0030||FO}} that contains mentions of both ({{arxiv_2411_12449_FO0031||FO}}, {{arxiv_2411_12449_FO0032||FO}}).